overview: Ultimate Video Gwarchive is a DVD collection of almost all of Gwar's videos up through the Violence Has Arrived album. The only ones not included are the Hell-O bonus track version of "Black & Huge", and "SFW". The cover art was designed by Chris Bopst, who played the original Balsac on bass guitar from 1985-1987.
title: Gwar ‎– Ultimate Video GWARchive
